incidents.name: 6/3 - 03:50 - 05:00 Boost UK Production Incident - Clickout to partnerts errors

incident_updates.body:
Hi All,

Last Night between ~ 03:50 - 05:00 We addressed a serving incident on our UK GEO. 

Visitors reaching our sites from UK/EU locations randomly reached and error page instead of being directed to the partner site.

The impact is that ~40% of the paid clicks (213 clicks) did not reach the partner site.

Automatic alert were triggered and TS + Devops addressed the incident by 05:00

We will conduct a review of this issue in order to better understand the root cause and advise on possible solutions.

TS Ticket: https://jira.naturalint.com/browse/TS-7483

incidents.name: Delay in DataOps Reporting - Revenue ETL expected to be available by ~18:00

incident_updates.body: This incident has been resolved.

Hi All,

Today's  11:30 Revenue ETL failed to complete and the next update of Revenue is expected to be by ~18:00 as part of the 14:30 revenue ETL run which is running at the moment.

The issue caused a delay in  DataOPS revenue reporting schedule.

Sorry for the inconvenience caused.
This incident has been resolved - all Postbacks are refreshed successfully effective 2/3.
